      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, mated to a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. The engine exhibits strong compression and linear power delivery across the rev range. Mechanical upgrades include a reinforced VANOS system and a subframe that has been inspected for structural integrity. The chassis is sorted with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and neutral balance these cars are known for. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the limited-slip differential and cooling system are in excellent working order. This is a mechanically robust machine ready for spirited canyon runs.",
